  "prompt": "What do we call video with words on it?",
  "response": "Video with words on it is commonly referred to as \"text overlay\" or \"captioned video.\" It can also be called \"subtitled video\" if the words are translations of spoken dialogue. Additionally, videos featuring presented text, such as quotes or messages, can be known as \"text videos\" or simply \"text animations\" if they emphasize visual text elements.",
